name: Mailman
description:
Your delivery is here!!
This is a model that's based on the everything postal including uniforms, vehicles, mailboxes and so on. Tends to work best at 0.6. This model was trained on NAI anime-full-pruned and generated in AOM3. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training through google colab.
